          "reviewBody": "Low focus on academics for classes like 9th , 10th . Poor planning . Industrial visits 2 days before final exams . No preparation holidays given. \nHigh fee, zero planning\nNo yearly calenders. Principal doesn't take parents feedback. Instead points back at students and parents\n\nSuggest not to join you children from grades above 6th .  Not worth to be an international school\n",
          "publisher": {
