          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Excellent institution, I realized the fact just in an academic year after my son's entry into this institution, He is here for the last 3years,\nEarlier, before joined to this institution, I used to change the schools (for my son) every year as the institutions didn't standby their words and promises,\nbut here in INTELLI , the management and the staff take utmost care of each and every child to make them complete in  both academics as well as personality development.\nThe management and the staff take each event serious and challenging to implement even though it's a small like revision sessions  for any exams, they conduct special classes for this, it's no where else.\nIt's unbelievable that the children are been provided Basel seeds /lemon water frequently (without any charges)to keep our children health.\nThe only institution I found in vizag after having deep survey with friends, colleagues and children, I found only a  'GNANASHALA'' (the name suits exactly)the space where importance is given to learning the things followed by applying in real life which develops the children skills,\nThe curriculum and teaching methods that they follow are wonderful ,each children enjoy the subjects and learning process, they never feel pressure ,\nI realized all of these best things in my son after joining to the Intelli family.\n\nIt's confirmed that the children pass out from this institution will become  successful , respectable individuals with high talents in the society with better positions.\n\nThe institution looks towards excellence which is above the success level.\n\nThank you\nTeam Intelli",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
